item.title: Going to live as digital Normad
item.description:
Going to live as digital Normad

After a lot of changes and thoughts, i decided that i will change my work-live balance and way of working. Since i was little i dream about traveling. But as a young mother, i didn't have the money, i didn't have the possibility. Even if live was tough as young mother, i have made it. Now after 12 years of freelancing as frontenddeveloper and Â specialized in TYPO3, managing a lot of projects i ask my self how live should go on.
